00:00:10.844 --> 00:00:12.303 position:50% align:center
[HIRO screaming]

00:00:12.387 --> 00:00:16.975 position:50% align:center
Don't do this!

00:00:17.058 --> 00:00:18.977 position:50% align:center
[panting]

00:00:20.645 --> 00:00:23.606 position:50% align:center
